{"tid":1967456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不再物競天擇當防疫？Boris Johnson步行做復健：與其他患者有共感","createTime":"2020-04-11T03:03:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T05:16:13.000Z","uid":28114,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5d3863898f58aa5061df2c71a1982d0a7bd1ab2","tid":1967456,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:03:29.000Z","msg":"英國首相強生（Boris Johnson）確診武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）後於上周日住進加護病房，並在10日時病情改善轉至一般病房，據了解目前強生可以短站的步行以作為復健。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/11/03/2222292-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F11%2F03%2F2222292-XXL.jpg&h=e1a5cfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲強生上個月26日確診武漢肺炎。（圖／翻攝自Boris Johnson臉書）<br />\n<br />\n英國首相強生在確診武漢肺炎後於上周日進入加護病房，令全球都緊張關注，根據唐寧街發言人表示，強生已於10日離開加護病房，轉至一般病房，並且能夠以短時間的步行做為康復的療程之一，「強生已經與醫生對談，並且相當感謝醫療團隊提供的完善照顧」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/01/14/2359849-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach-setn-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F01%2F14%2F2359849-XXL.jpg&h=5f9ca240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲10日轉出加護病房。（圖／翻攝自Boris Johnson臉書）<br />\n<br />\n由於過去強生輕視武漢肺炎，曾提出「民眾如果有持續咳嗽或高溫症狀，應該要先自己在家隔離，醫療單位對於輕症不進行檢測，因此民眾只能自我隔離7天，如果病況惡化才撥打急診專線送醫院。」當時這樣的說法被許多人直指是「物競天擇」的防疫方式，然而在離開加護病房後，唐寧街的發言人表示「強生與其他患者感同身受。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?NewsID=723630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D723630&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VR21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=fd4bca2a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fnews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D723630&h=a20d79bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/news.aspx?NewsID=723630</a>"},{"pid":"b47d421497d7fd88f14ebdcb81456c78494068cf","tid":1967456,"uid":132898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:11:26.000Z","msg":"食過屎先知屎係臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479f43da7f4013d794228dfaff1c843d9b850ca0","tid":1967456,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab57d3d188e30be082e4d83d3bc694d8d23f0db1","tid":1967456,"uid":41355,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"好似gphone咁<br />\n坐完之後人生唔同晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa8c242cb86ddf41c22ee853ad487e13c2ab4e3","tid":1967456,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"唔知跳起有冇1cm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW奶共後果"},{"pid":"5f664b737d6eb1ab757d87f8905aaa273c6bc40a","tid":1967456,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:43:53.000Z","msg":"希望你病完中過招會聯合排共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d02c14da4a9eeb9940b46fb953593df02f77b6","tid":1967456,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:47:42.000Z","msg":"係咪想扮黑暗對峙坐地鐵o個幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n奶共抵仆街"},{"pid":"7cadfb0c0b2c7a284024fc4f52d547d24bd5055d","tid":1967456,"uid":269515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T04:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kyceFnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkyceFnF.jpg&h=3d821449&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zV6V9f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzV6V9f0.jpg&h=91c4b388&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"811934b9bd46e42deb01850f1cc2b41